<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

{{> header title ="invitation deleted"}}
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <div class="logo-icon">G</div>
                <div class="logo-text">GradPal</div>
            </div>
            <h1 class="header-title">Service Invitation Update</h1>
            <div class="status-badge">‚ö†Ô∏è Invitation Cancelled</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Dear Student,
            </div>

            <div class="main-message">
                We're writing to inform you that an invitation to join an autonomous learning service has been
                cancelled. While this particular opportunity is no longer available, we want to keep you informed and
                help you explore other learning options.
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-title">{{serviceTitle}}</div>

                <div class="service-detail">
                    <div class="service-label">Teacher:</div>
                    <div class="service-value">{{teacherName}}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-detail">
                    <div class="service-label">Subject:</div>
                    <div class="service-value">
                        <span class="subject-badge">{{subject}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-detail">
                    <div class="service-label">Status:</div>
                    <div class="service-value">Invitation Cancelled</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cancellation-notice">
                <div class="cancellation-icon">üìã</div>
                <div class="cancellation-title">Invitation No Longer Available</div>
                <div class="cancellation-text">
                    This service invitation has been removed by the teacher. This could be due to capacity limits,
                    schedule changes, or other administrative reasons.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="alternatives-section">
                <div class="alternatives-title">Don't worry! Here are your options:</div>
                <ul class="alternatives-list">
                    <li>Browse other available services in the same subject area</li>
                    <li>Contact your teacher directly to discuss alternative learning opportunities</li>
                    <li>Explore our catalog of autonomous learning services</li>
                    <li>Set up notifications for similar services that become available</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="main-message">
                We understand this might be disappointing, but there are many other excellent learning opportunities
                available on GradPal. Our team is committed to helping you find the perfect learning experience that
                matches your needs and goals.
            </div>

            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="#" class="cta-button">Browse Available Services</a>
                <a href="#" class="cta-button secondary">Contact Support</a>
            </div>

            <div class="main-message">
                <strong>Questions or concerns?</strong><br>
                Our support team is here to help you navigate this change and find alternative learning opportunities
                that align with your educational goals.
            </div>
        </div>

        {{> footer NationalPortal=NationalPortal}}
    </div>
</body>

</html>